// Absolute file Path and Relative File Path//

/(root) --> work(Folder) ---> report.doc(file) , Project(Folder) ----> talk.ppt

#The Absolute File Path Is: /work/Project/talk.ppt

#The Relative File Path Assuming we are in Project folder : ./talk.ppt
                                           work folder : ./Project/talk.ppt

Here ./ represents to check in current file...

#To access report.doc from Project Folder: ../report.doc

Here ../ Takes Us To Parent Folder (Which Is Work for Project Folder)....
